[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0638","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0638.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0844","title":"Deerfield MDaemon URL 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Deerfield MDaemon 2.8.5 及 2.8.6 版本（以及 Alt-N WorldClient Pro/Standard 2.0.0.x）的 Web 服务组件在处理超长 URL 请求时存在缓冲区处理缺陷，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向目标服务器发送特制长 URL 请求触发服务崩溃，导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 MDaemon 邮件服务器的 Web 管理界面与 WorldClient Webmail 组件，攻击复杂度低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0844"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-24","updated":"1999-11-24","remediation":"建议立即升级 MDaemon 至 2.8.7 或更高版本，该版本修复了 URL 处理中的缓冲区边界检查缺陷。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙层面限制对 WorldClient（端口 2000）和 WebConfig（端口 2002）的访问，仅允许受信任 IP 连接，或部署反向代理限制 URL 长度以临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19640"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0638.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0786","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0786.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0980","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Service Control Manager 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 服务控制管理器（SCM）在处理资源枚举请求时存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送包含畸形参数的资源枚举请求触发 Services.exe 进程崩溃，导致系统服务拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 SP1 至 SP6 所有版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程发起攻击，仅需向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求即可触发 Services.exe 进程崩溃，导致系统服务停止响应，需重启系统恢复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0980"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-23","updated":"2026-07-14","remediation":"立即升级到 Windows NT 4.0 SP6a（MS99-055 安全公告）或更高版本；若已无法升级，建议迁移到 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本，同时在网络边界过滤 SMB/RPC 端口并关闭不必要的服务以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-055","http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb;%5BLN%5D;Q246045","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19578"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0786.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0911","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0911.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1058","title":"Vermillion FTP Daemon 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Vermillion FTP Daemon VFTPD 1.23 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 FTP 服务器发送多个特制的超长 CWD 命令触发该漏洞，导致服务进程崩溃引发拒绝服务，在特定条件下甚至可能执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 VFTPD 1.23 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，建议升级或限制访问以降低风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1058"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.050","remediation":"立即停止使用已停止维护的 Vermillion FTP Daemon VFTPD 1.23，迁移至现代活跃维护的 FTP 服务器（如 vsftpd 或 ProFTPD），或在条件允许时改用 SFTP/FTPS 替代 FTP 协议。如暂时无法迁移，应在网络边界防火墙限制对 FTP 端口（默认 21）的访问来源 IP，并使用 IPS/IDS 规则检测并阻断超长 CWD 命令（正常 CWD 路径长度通常不超过 256 字符）以缓解缓冲区溢出风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94329968617085&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=94337185023159&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/818","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3543","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1058.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1058","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1058.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1058.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1058.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7cj6-wm7r-4g46/GHSA-7cj6-wm7r-4g46.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/V/vftpd_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/818/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1058.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0911.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0580","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0580.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0818","title":"Sun Solaris 7.0 kcms_configure NETPATH 环境变量缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 7.0 系统中的 kcms_configure 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过设置超长的 NETPATH 环境变量触发该漏洞，导致权限提升，获取 root 级别系统控制权。该漏洞影响 Solaris 7.0 版本，攻击者需要本地 shell 权限即可利用，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0818"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.333","remediation":"从 Sun（甲骨文）获取并安装 Solaris 7 对应补丁（如 Patch ID 107081-xx 等 kcms_configure 相关补丁集）；若无法打补丁，立即移除 kcms_configure 的 setuid root 权限位（chmod u-s /usr/dt/bin/kcms_configure），该操作可阻断本地提权利用，或升级至 Solaris 8 及以上版本以彻底修复此缓冲区溢出漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/831","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=38433B7F5A.53F4SHADOWPENGUIN%40fox.nightland.net","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19647"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0580.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0580.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0580.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0617","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0617.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0831","title":"Linux Kernel Syslog 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux syslogd 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 syslog 服务发送大量网络连接请求，耗尽系统日志处理资源，导致 syslogd 崩溃或停止响应，无法正常记录日志。该漏洞影响多个 Linux 发行版本，攻击条件简单，无需身份认证即可实施攻击，危害等级中等。建议升级版本或限制网络访问以缓解风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0831"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:08.923","remediation":"升级 sysklogd 至 1.3 及以上版本（该版本修复了并发连接处理缺陷）；若使用 Caldera OpenLinux，安装 CSSA-1999-035.0 安全补丁。现代环境建议迁移至 rsyslog 或 syslog-ng 替代传统 syslogd，并在防火墙层面限制 UDP/TCP 514 端口的来源 IP 范围，仅允许受信日志发送端访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/809"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0617.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0832","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0832.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0999","title":"Microsoft SQL Server 7.0 TDS Packet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft SQL Server 7.0 在处理 TDS（Tabular Data Stream）协议数据包时存在输入验证不足漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器发送特制的空数据（NULL Data）TDS 报文，导致 SQL Server 服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Microsoft SQL Server 7.0 及 7.0 SP1 版本，CVSS 评分 4.3，危害等级中危。Microsoft 已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0999"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.610","remediation":"建议立即升级到 Microsoft SQL Server 7.0 Service Pack 2（SP2）或更高版本，该更新修复了 TDS 协议数据包畸形输入校验缺陷。如无法升级，可在网络边界防火墙配置规则过滤对 1433/TCP 端口的非授权访问，并限制可信来源 IP 以降低远程攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ248749","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/817","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-059","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19638","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0999.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0999.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0999","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0999.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0999.json","https://github.com/morpheuslord/CVE-llm_dataset/blob/91b337d05c623a68829de977c2b1ae6c0f91702b/README.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/mssqlserver_dos.nasl","https://github.com/dependency-check/DependencyCheck/blob/8119dd0f6e121ff60c6eaace2de1791c2a81c41d/core/src/main/resources/dependencycheck-base-suppression.xml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cj38-2rjc-pv2v/GHSA-cj38-2rjc-pv2v.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0832.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1600","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1600.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0987","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 安全策略绕过漏洞","description":"Windows NT 域认证机制存在安全缺陷，当域用户在登录时输入的域名末尾包含空格字符，系统无法正确下载并应用域安全策略，导致绕过身份认证。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，攻击者只需拥有域账户，通过在域名后附加空格即可触发。利用方式简单，危害等级严重，CVSS 评分 10.0。微软已发布安全更新修复此问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0987"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.090","remediation":"建议立即升级 Windows NT 4.0 至 Service Pack 6a 或更高版本，该补丁（KB Q237923）修复了域登录时尾部空格导致策略下载失败的问题。对于无法升级的系统，应在登录流程入口处对域名字段做 Trim 处理，去除首尾空白字符，并确保域控制器和客户端统一校验域名格式。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ237923","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/3701042200a4e64b9e2a7f3614e9e958db6af9cd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0987","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0987.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--1e5167f2-8c39-4729-bfeb-a8843e869244.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/fef2105ce9bc36a63673a5e0577e307a0953c8a8/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1600.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0528","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0528.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0793","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer JavaScript URL 重定向漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0.1 及 5.0 版本中存在 JavaScript URL 重定向漏洞。远程攻击者可构造特制恶意网页，通过 JavaScript 将浏览器窗口重定向至 `file://` 协议的本地文件系统 URL，从而绕过同源策略的跨域限制，实现跨协议脚本执行。成功利用此漏洞的攻击者能够读取目标用户计算机上的任意本地文件内容，可能导致敏感信息泄露。攻击条件简单，仅需诱使用户使用受影响版本 IE 浏览器访问恶意网页即可触发，无需任何用户交互或额外权限。微软已通过 MS99-043 安全公告提供修复补丁。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0793"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:04.173","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-043 提供的修补程序，或升级到 Internet Explorer 5.01 及以上版本。对于无法升级的旧系统，可通过禁用 Active Scripting 和限制 Internet 区域权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-043","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19559"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0528.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0528.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0935","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0935.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1092","title":"tin 1.40 权限配置不当本地信息泄露漏洞","description":"tin 1.40（一个Usenet新闻阅读器）在创建用户配置文件目录 `.tin` 时使用了不安全的默认权限，导致同一系统上的其他本地用户可读取该目录下的 `.inputhistory` 文件。该文件存储了用户登录新闻服务器时输入的密码等敏感信息，攻击者只需拥有本地普通用户权限即可窃取其他用户的凭据，进而访问受保护的新闻服务器资源。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1092"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.303","remediation":"升级 tin 至 1.41 或更高版本，该版本已修复 .tin 目录权限问题。若无法升级，手动执行 `chmod 700 ~/.tin` 限制目录权限，并删除或移走 ~/.tin/.inputhistory 文件（或使用 `chmod 600 ~/.tin/.inputhistory` 限制该文件仅所有者可读写），防止其他本地用户读取存储的密码信息。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94286179032648&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1092.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1092","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1092.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1092.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1092.json","https://github.com/SAP/fosstars-rating-core/blob/7b172f42f218f6cfad42f81bd9c9ef49de35b919/docs/oss/security/google/tink.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1092.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88535/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000883.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0935.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0935.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0935.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0903","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0903.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1051","title":"Matt Wright FormHandler.cgi 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Matt Wright FormHandler.cgi 脚本的默认配置存在目录限制缺陷，仅对 /etc/ 目录进行了访问限制，未对其他目录做有效过滤。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过 reply_message_attach 参数指定任意文件路径，导致服务器上任意文件被读取，包括配置文件、源码等敏感信息。该漏洞影响使用默认配置部署 FormHandler.cgi 的 Web 服务器，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1051"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.223","remediation":"立即删除或停用 FormHandler.cgi 脚本，该脚本已不再维护且存在设计缺陷。如必须使用，编辑脚本源码，将附件的基路径硬编码为固定安全目录（如 /var/lib/formhandler/attachments/），并严格校验 reply_message_attach 参数值，拒绝包含 \"../\" 等路径回溯字符的输入。同时配置 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）限制 CGI 目录下仅允许 POST 方法访问该脚本，禁止直接通过 GET 参数读取任意路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34939","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1051.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1051","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1051.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1051.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1051.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6vh4-w25v-6gh9/GHSA-6vh4-w25v-6gh9.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88494/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1051.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0903.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1777","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1777.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1190","title":"Admiral Systems EmailClub POP3 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Admiral Systems EmailClub 1.05 的 POP3 服务器存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标电子邮件地址发送包含超长 \"From\" 头部的恶意邮件，触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。攻击无需身份认证，利用复杂度低，可完全控制受影响系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1190"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-15","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议立即停用 Admiral Systems EmailClub 1.0.0.5，该产品已达生命周期且厂商已不再维护。应迁移至受支持的邮件服务器软件（如 Dovecot、Cyrus IMAP），并在网络边界限制对 POP3 端口（110/TCP）的访问，仅允许可信源 IP。若无法立即替换，部署入侵检测规则拦截超长 From 头部的邮件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securiteam.com/exploits/E-MailClub__FROM__remote_buffer_overflow.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/801","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19621"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1777.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0951","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0951.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1110","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 Media Player ActiveX 文件存在性信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows Media Player ActiveX 控件在 Internet Explorer 5.0 中被调用时，当指定文件不存在会返回特定错误码，导致存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者可构造恶意网页，通过脚本调用该 ActiveX 对象并捕获返回的错误信息，从而探测目标系统上任意文件是否存在，威胁用户隐私安全。该漏洞仅影响安装了 Windows Media Player 的 Internet Explorer 5 用户。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1110"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.477","remediation":"升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.01 Service Pack 2 以上版本，或安装 Microsoft 安全更新 MS00-009 对应补丁。如无法升级，在注册表 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\ActiveX Compatibility 中为 Windows Media Player ActiveX 控件 CLSID 设置兼容性标志 (Flags=0x400) 以禁用 Kill Bit，阻止其在 IE 中加载。同时建议将 IE 升级至 6.0 及以上版本以彻底消除该风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34675","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/793","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19618","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1110.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1110.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1110","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1110.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1110.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1110.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mhq8-h8mw-8cgr/GHSA-mhq8-h8mw-8cgr.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1110.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000876.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0951.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0951.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0951.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0901","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0901.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1050","title":"Matt Wright FormHandler.cgi 2.0 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Matt Wright 开发的 FormHandler.cgi 2.0 脚本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 reply_message_attach 参数传入 ../ 等路径穿越序列，或直接指定模板文件名为目标文件路径，从而读取服务器上的任意敏感文件。该漏洞影响 FormHandler.cgi 2.0 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1050"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.070","remediation":"建议立即从 Web 服务器中移除或停用 `FormHandler.cgi` 脚本，改用受支持的上传组件。若无法移除，可在 Perl 脚本入口处增加路径规范化校验：使用 `File::Spec->rel2abs` 解析真实路径并检查是否越界到 Web 根目录之外；同时过滤用户输入中的 `..` 和 `/` 字符，并设置严格的模板白名单。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34600","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34939","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/798","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/799","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3550","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19620","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1050.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1050","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1050.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1050.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1050.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rrx8-7p59-h436/GHSA-rrx8-7p59-h436.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/F/formhandler.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/798/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1050.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000873.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0901.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0618","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0618.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0833","title":"ISC BIND 8.2 NXT 记录处理缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"BIND 8.2 在处理 NXT 资源记录时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可向运行 BIND 8.2 的 DNS 服务器发送特制的 NXT 记录数据包，触发缓冲区溢出，导致 DNS 服务进程崩溃或执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行 BIND 8.2 版本的 Solaris 及其他 Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。建议升级至 BIND 8.2 以上的修复版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0833"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:09.190","remediation":"将 BIND 升级至 8.2.1 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙或 TCP Wrappers 中限制对 DNS 服务（端口 53/UDP+TCP）的访问来源，仅允许受信任的 IP 段发起查询。同时禁用递归查询（`options { recursion no; };`）以降低被利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/788"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0618.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0647","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0647.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0848","title":"ISC BIND 8.2/8.2.1 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"ISC BIND 8.2 及 8.2.1 版本的域名服务进程 named 存在文件描述符管理缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送大量特制的 DNS 查询请求，消耗超过 \"fdmax\" 限制的文件描述符数量，导致 named 进程耗尽系统资源而崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响运行 ISC BIND 8.2/8.2.1 的系统，包括 IRIX 6.5.17 和 Solaris 7.0 等平台，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0848"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:11.040","remediation":"升级到 ISC BIND 8.2.2 及以上版本，该版本修复了 fdmax 文件描述符耗尽导致的拒绝服务问题。若无法升级，可在系统层面限制 named 进程可打开的文件描述符数量（ulimit -n），并监控系统日志中异常的连接请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/194","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/788","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19615"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0647.toml"}]